options.query:
SELECT 
    TO_CHAR(MIN(date_of_submission), 'DD/MM/YYYY') AS min_date, 
    TO_CHAR(MAX(date_of_submission), 'DD/MM/YYYY') AS max_date 
FROM 
    business_data;

SELECT DISTINCT LOWER(gender) AS lower_entity,
    INITCAP(gender) AS initcap_entity
FROM business_data
ORDER BY lower_entity;

SELECT DISTINCT LOWER(context_aspect_group) AS lower_entity,
    INITCAP(context_aspect_group) AS initcap_entity
FROM business_data
ORDER BY lower_entity;

CREATE TABLE business_data(
    brand text,
    source text,
    aspect text,
    context_aspect_group text,
    date_of_submission date,
    gender text,
    roa text,
    overall_sentiment text
);

SELECT DISTINCT LOWER(source) AS lower_entity,
    INITCAP(source) AS initcap_entity
FROM business_data
ORDER BY lower_entity;

{{`WITH months AS (
    SELECT
        generate_series(
            '${moment(components.datepicker1.value, "DD/MM/YYYY").format("YYYY-MM-DD")}' :: date,
            '${moment(components.datepicker2.value, "DD/MM/YYYY").format("YYYY-MM-DD")}' :: date,
            '1 month' :: interval
        ) AS month
),
enitites AS (
    SELECT
        DISTINCT LOWER(${ components.dropdown2.value }) as ${ components.dropdown2.value }
    FROM
        business_data
    WHERE
        LOWER(${ components.dropdown2.value }) IN ('${(components.dropdown2.value == "brand" ? components.multiselect5.values : components.multiselect6.values).join("', '")}')
)
SELECT
    TO_CHAR(m.month, 'Mon YY') AS month_year,
    INITCAP(LOWER(e.${ components.dropdown2.value })) AS entity,
    COUNT(cd.${ components.dropdown2.value }) AS total_reviews,
    COUNT(
        CASE
            WHEN cd.overall_sentiment = 'Positive' THEN 1
        END
    ) AS positive_reviews
FROM
    months m
    CROSS JOIN enitites e
    LEFT JOIN business_data cd ON TO_CHAR(cd.date_of_submission, 'Mon YY') = TO_CHAR(m.month, 'Mon YY')
    AND LOWER(cd.${ components.dropdown2.value }) = LOWER(e.${ components.dropdown2.value })
    AND LOWER(cd.brand) in ('${components.multiselect5.values.join("', '")}')
    AND LOWER(cd.source) in ('${components.multiselect6.values.join("', '")}')
    AND LOWER(cd.roa) in ('${components.multiselect7.values.join("', '")}')
    AND LOWER(cd.gender) in ('${components.multiselect8.values.join("', '")}')
GROUP BY
    TO_CHAR(m.month, 'Mon YY'),
    LOWER(e.${ components.dropdown2.value })
ORDER BY
    TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(m.month, 'Mon YY'), 'Mon YY'),
    LOWER(e.${ components.dropdown2.value });`}}

SELECT DISTINCT LOWER(brand) AS lower_entity,
    INITCAP(brand) AS initcap_entity
FROM business_data
ORDER BY lower_entity;

SELECT DISTINCT LOWER(roa) AS lower_entity,
    INITCAP(roa) AS initcap_entity
FROM business_data
ORDER BY lower_entity;

{{`SELECT
    INITCAP(${ components.dropdown2.value }) AS entity,
    SUM(
        CASE
            WHEN overall_sentiment = 'Positive' THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END
    ) AS positive_reviews,
    SUM(
        CASE
            WHEN overall_sentiment = 'Negative' THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END
    ) AS negative_reviews,
    SUM(
        CASE
            WHEN overall_sentiment = 'Neutral' THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END
    ) AS neutral_reviews,
    COUNT(*) AS total_reviews
FROM
    business_data
WHERE
    date_of_submission BETWEEN '${moment(components.datepicker1.value, "DD/MM/YYYY").format("YYYY-MM-DD")}'
    AND '${moment(components.datepicker2.value, "DD/MM/YYYY").format("YYYY-MM-DD")}'
    AND LOWER(brand) in ('${components.multiselect5.values.join("', '")}')
    AND LOWER(source) in ('${components.multiselect6.values.join("', '")}')
    AND LOWER(roa) in ('${components.multiselect7.values.join("', '")}')
    AND LOWER(gender) in ('${components.multiselect8.values.join("', '")}')
GROUP BY
    ${ components.dropdown2.value }
ORDER BY
    total_reviews ASC;`}}
